   </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>ZOMBIE ATTACK 게임 시작 화면</em></p>\n<br>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<p>Unity Asset Store에 등록되어 있는 3D 모델을 다운받아 좀비와 1인칭 사람에 움직일 수 있도록 애니메이션을 적용했습니다. 좀비는 자동적으로 움직일 수 있도록 설정해 놓았으며 1인칭인 사람은 키보드 A(오른쪽), D(왼쪽), W(직진), S(후진)으로 움직일 수 있습니다. 총과 총알을 다운받아 C#으로 마우스의 왼쪽을 누르면 총알이 나갈 수 있도록 구현했습니다.<br>\n<br></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 799px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/6efb5/select.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.09386733416771%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/01472/select.webp 240w,\n/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/222bd/select.webp 480w,\n/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/c75f7/select.webp 799w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 799px) 100vw, 799px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/3bc27/select.jpg 240w,\n/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/98431/select.jpg 480w,\n/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/6efb5/select.jpg 799w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 799px) 100vw, 799px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/910337a5b814ebecc4abd61a6113806b/6efb5/select.jpg\"\n          alt=\"select.JPG\"\n          title=\"select.JPG\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[ Game Strart ]버튼을 누르면 3가지 총 디자인 중 본인이<br>원하는 총을 선택하여 좀비와 싸울 수 있습니다.</p>\n<br>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 797px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/ab18c/game.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.65495608531995%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/01472/game.webp 240w,\n/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/222bd/game.webp 480w,\n/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/6579e/game.webp 797w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 797px) 100vw, 797px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/3bc27/game.jpg 240w,\n/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/98431/game.jpg 480w,\n/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/ab18c/game.jpg 797w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 797px) 100vw, 797px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/785e44ee0006876ec9526eba151732bc/ab18c/game.jpg\"\n          alt=\"game.JPG\"\n          title=\"game.JPG\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 802px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/5421d/attack.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.3142144638404%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/01472/attack.webp 240w,\n/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/222bd/attack.webp 480w,\n/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/43b8e/attack.webp 802w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 802px) 100vw, 802px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/3bc27/attack.jpg 240w,\n/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/98431/attack.jpg 480w,\n/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/5421d/attack.jpg 802w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 802px) 100vw, 802px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/3aecf63746a0cf8cf55e23d395e4c487/5421d/attack.jpg\"\n          alt=\"attack.JPG\"\n          title=\"attack.JPG\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>좀비를 3명 이상을 죽여야 게임을 성공하며 죽일 때마다 점수가 올라 총 60점 맞아야 게임에서 이기게 됩니다.\n<br>\n<br>\n좀비에게 닿으면 HP가 깎이며 시작 100HP에서 0HP가<br>되면 죽게됩니다.\n<br>\n<br>\n오른쪽 하단의 숫자 / 무한의 표시는 총알의 갯수를 표현한 것 입니다.</p>\n<br>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 796px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e3116976e486e2d12d2146ba28018a9/a53a2/success.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n   