,\n/static/6619a05cd5647c3f644d470a83ee4933/98431/fail.jpg 480w,\n/static/6619a05cd5647c3f644d470a83ee4933/ab18c/fail.jpg 797w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 797px) 100vw, 797px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/6619a05cd5647c3f644d470a83ee4933/ab18c/fail.jpg\"\n          alt=\"fail.JPG\"\n          title=\"fail.JPG\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>게임의 성공과 실패화면 입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Zombie-Attack/","tagSlugs":["/tag/unity-3-d/","/tag/c/","/tag/javascript/","/tag/photoshop/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2015-11-01T22:40:32.169Z","description":"Unity 3D와 C#을 활용하여 좀비를 피해 총으로 맞춰 살아남는 1인용 FPS총 게임입니다.","tags":["Unity 3D","C#","Javascript","Photoshop"],"title":"ZOMBIE ATTACK 1인용 FPS 총 게임","socialImage":"/media/zombie-attack/zombie_main.JPG"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/Zombie-Attack/"}}}